    kicker: `Stunts &amp; Action · <b>Core Craft</b>`,
    dek: `The fall that looks fatal, the bullet hit that spurts blood — these impact effects are some of action's most visceral moments, and among the most tightly engineered. Understanding how high falls and squibs really work shows you both why they're professional-only and how much of their power comes from clever, safe technique rather than real danger.`,
